	   <tr><td colspan=2>I agree that this scedule can work.  However, you are very equipped to go into Lava Storm mountains at level 12 and setup shop at the Najena entrance.  As long as you stick close to the Najena zone you will make good money and level quickly.  Fire drakes are very easy at level 12, also there will be many Dervishes and Elementals that will con white/Black and yellow to you.  Make sure you use your water elemental, renew elements, ward summoning, and other DD's.  Also bind yourself in Nektulos right before the Lava Storm zone line.. it makes travel very fast when selling and less dangerous.  This strategy has everything I have wanted so far.  Great XP, Good money, easy travel to selling/training/spells, and it's EXCITING all of the time = )  Plus you have high level characters coming in and out of Najena who usually will toss a couple buffs on you.  Just make sure, if it seems like it's going to be close, you haul arse up the ramp and zone.  Try not to leave the area just outside either.  Stick near the ramp.<br><br>Good luck<br><br>Cyiboath 13th level Mage<br> Fenin Ro<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
