	   <tr><td colspan=2>UM, no....there already IS a spot in rathe mountains for a mages as low as 34. In rathe mountains there are two troll guards standing near a tower. They are both level 35. The one on the left is a shadowknight. The one on the right is a shaman. You will be fighting the shaman. It is pretty simple to kill her. Pretty much just a straight send pet and nuke. After she dies her wolf pet will be left, but it isn't much of a problem, your pet at 20% health could kill it and live. The guards do not help each other, if you pull them from far enough away. Once you get to level 39 you can start killing hill giants in Rathe Mountains or you can stay at the troll guards and start killing both of them. At 39 you won't be able to keep up with both the spawns, but you will be able to take both of them off and on. Once you get to 44 the hill giants are still great exp. OR you can still stay at the guards and start camping both at once.<br><br>Hope that helps.<br><br>Former EQ Addict.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
